metadata.name: Mr Sheep #1
metadata.description: Mr Sheep Club is a collection of 10,000 programmatically generated unique NFTs that exist on Ethereum Blockchain. Each Mr Sheep is unique - just like you - and generated from many different traits, including clothing, skin, expression, and more. Mr Sheep holders will join the Club and participate in exclusive events such as airdrops, massive giveaways and much more.  There will be also a new 3D Mr Sheep Collection and Mr Sheep Video game release. Join an ambitious ever-growing community with multiple benefits and utilities. Be sure to check out our Roadmap to see all great and exciting opportunities!                http://mrsheep.info/
